ORCHARD ESTATE HOMES
v.
The ORCHARD HOMEOWNER ALLIANCE S255031 Supreme Court of California. JUNE 19, 2019

Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar, Kruger and Groban, JJ.

The request for judicial notice is granted as to exhibits B and C, and is denied as to exhibit. The petition for review is granted. The request for an order directing depublication of the opinion is denied.
